## Map
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map R reload
map o Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map O Vomnibar.activate
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map B Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map tl Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map T Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map < goBack
map > goForward
map u scrollUp
map e scrollDown
map U scrollUp count=6.5 #scrollFullPageUp
#map U scrollFullPageUp
map E scrollDown count=6.5 #FullPageDown
#map E scrollFullPageDown
map n scrollLeft
map i scrollRight
map Q removeTab
map ti nextTab
map . nextTab
map tn previousTab
map , previousTab
map tu createTab
map te moveTabToNewWindow
map tmn moveTabLeft
map tmi moveTabRight
map = performFind
map - performBackwardsFind
map k focusInput
map v enterVisualMode
map V enterVisualLineMode
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode
